--------------------------------
Unit testing MyCounter C++ class
--------------------------------


Quick instructions for running the tests
----------------------------------------

1. Run test against faulty MyCounter:

   make clean; make FAULTY=1

2. Run test against working MyCounter:

   make clean; make


Files
-----

mycounter.h
mycounter.cc
        implementation of MyCounter, the unit under test

mycountertest.cc.aal
        unit test steps, tests are generated from these

asserts.h
        ASSERT-macros used in the unit tests

mycountertest.conf
        test configuration for running a unit test, defines test
        generation parameters and end conditions for the test

Makefile
        rules for building the unit under test, generating the test
        code (mycountertest.cc) from the AAL description, and running
        the test.
